                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        Helpful tools
                    </h2>
                    <p class="lead"><strong>Timer</strong>: The remaining time is always visible and an alarm will sound when the time is over.</p>
                    <p class="lead"><strong>Tags</strong>: By using tags, you can add contexts, organize and find your elements easily.</p>
                    <p class="lead"><strong>Collector</strong>: Capture your ideas and process them later on, releasing your mind for other tasks.</p>
                    <p class="lead"><strong>Browsers</strong>: Find your items by using search and autocomplete functionality, or just by browsing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-1 col-sm-6">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="/Content/img/landing/tools.png" alt="Tools">
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
